ZH: 他说的都是胡说八道。
EN: He's talking nonsense.

ZH: 别听他的，他总是乱胡说。
EN: Don't listen to him, he always talks nonsense.

ZH: 这完全是胡说八道。
EN: This is absolute nonsense.

ZH: 你不要再胡说了！
EN: Stop talking nonsense!

ZH: 他老是胡说八道，我们都不信他的话。
EN: He always talks nonsense, we don't believe anything he says.

ZH: 他没来得及准备，就开始胡说起来。
EN: He started talking nonsense without preparing beforehand.

ZH: 这是我听过的最荒谬的胡说。
EN: This is the most ridiculous nonsense I've ever heard.

ZH: 别听信这些胡说八道。
EN: Don't believe in these nonsenses.

ZH: 他今天糊涂了，都在乱胡说。
EN: He's confused today, he's just talking nonsense.

ZH: 他的理论完全是胡说。
EN: His theory is totally nonsense.

ZH: 你不要再胡说八道，听我的话。
EN: Stop talking nonsense and listen to me.

ZH: 老板发火了，因为他一个劲儿的胡说。
EN: The boss got angry because he just kept talking nonsense.

ZH: 别再胡说了，好好听别人说的话。
EN: Stop talking nonsense and listen to what others have to say.

ZH: 这种说法太胡说了。
EN: This argument is too nonsensical.

ZH: 他看见一只会说话的狗，觉得自己在做梦，以为是在胡说八道。
EN: He saw a talking dog and thought he was dreaming, thinking it was all nonsense.

ZH: 当初他们说的都是胡说。
EN: What they said back then was all nonsense.

ZH: 我曾经跟他讲过，别再胡说八道了。
EN: I've told him not to talk nonsense anymore.

ZH: 他的话全是胡说，没有一点真实性。
EN: His words are all nonsense, with no truth to them.

ZH: 他越说越乱，都是胡说八道。
EN: The more he talks, the more confused he gets, it's all nonsense.

ZH: 别再听他的胡说了，他总是编造事情。
EN: Don't listen to his nonsense anymore, he always makes things up.
